msIdentifier.repository: Kislak Center for Special Collections, Rare Books and Manuscripts

msContents.summary: Manuscript is used for consultation and study and is a philosophical discussion of time and the rules (Hindu law, dharma) that govern the performance of various religious observances, especially Vedic rituals.

msItem.title: Kālanirṇaya
कालनिर्णय
msItem.colophon: Colophon: iti śrīmādhavīye kālanirṇaye nakṣatrādi nirṇayākhyaṃ pamcamaṃ prakaraṇaṃ samāptam śubham astū (f. 175r).
